fitdist for CCME Boron Data

Source: R/data.R
fluazinam_lnorm.Rd

A fitdist object for Species Sensitivity Data for Boron with the lnorm distribution.

fluazinam_lnorm

Format

An object of class fitdistcens of length 17.

See also

fitdistrplus::fluazinam()
